Template: atlas-server/nginx
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Will you be using nginx?

Template: atlas-server/internal-port
Type: string
Default: 1400
Description: What port should the backend run on?
 This port should not be forwarded.

Template: atlas-server/external-port
Type: string
Default: 443
Description: What port should nginx use?

Template: atlas-server/https-hostname
Type: string
Description: Enter the hostname used for Let's Encrypt certificates.
 Leave blank to disable HTTPS.

Template: atlas-server/key
Type: string
Default: secret-key
Description: What is the key to the server?
 The backend will be available at https://frontend:port/key
